<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Salon Manager</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fdabab;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2em 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #cf97a0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .booking-details {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .booking-details h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #e681f0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .services-button {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fffafa;
        }

        .services-button:hover {
            background-color: #e681f0;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Salon Harmony</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="booking-details">
            <h2>Manage Your Salon Effectively</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Salon Harmony, your all-in-one solution for salon management. Keep track of bookings, manage
                services, and provide the best experience for your clients.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/home/bookings" class="button">View Bookings</a>
            <a href="/home/services" class="button services-button">Manage Services</a>
        </div>

        <p>Effortlessly streamline your salon operations with Salon Harmony. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
            adipiscing elit. Nullam tincidunt, justo eu vestibulum sollicitudin, tortor dui venenatis urna, eu aliquet
            elit ipsum in quam.</p>
    </main>
</body>

</html>